description:
This is a 29 minute workout called '30-Minute HIIT Cardio Workout with Warm Up - No Equipment at Home | SELF' from the channel SELF.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: In this high intensity cardio bodyweight workout from trainer Lita Lewis, you’ll spike your heart rate with high-knees, fast feet, and star jumps; plus work your core and lower body with jumping lunges and planks - at home! No equipment needed!
